show.description: A modest home cook marries a man she believes is ordinary—unaware he’s a billionaire testing the power of true love. As she endures cruel humiliation and desperately searches for her missing daughter, a stunning truth comes to light. A saga of hidden identities, family betrayal, and unshakable love—where heartbreak meets redemption.
